### Get hello world text
GET http://localhost:5000/text
Accept: application/json

### Get hello for a specific user
GET http://localhost:5000/text/JohnDoe
Accept: application/json

### --- BEER ENDPOINTS ---

### Get all beers
GET http://localhost:5000/beers
Accept: application/json

### Get beer by id
GET http://localhost:5000/beers/1
Accept: application/json


### Create one or more beers

POST http://localhost:5000/beers
Content-Type: application/json

[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"name": "Sample Beer",
		"type": "Lager",
		"alcoholContent": 5.0
	},
	{
		"id": 0,
		"name": "Another Beer",
		"type": "Ale",
		"alcoholContent": 6.0
	}
]

### Create a single beer (also valid)

POST http://localhost:5000/beers
Content-Type: application/json

[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"name": "Single Beer",
		"type": "Stout",
		"alcoholContent": 7.0
	},
    {
        "id": 1,
        "name": "Second Beer",
        "type": "Pilsner",
        "alcoholContent": 4.5
    }
]

### Update a beer
PUT http://localhost:5000/beers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"id": 1,
	"name": "Updated Beer",
	"type": "Ale",
	"alcoholContent": 6.0
}

### Delete a beer
DELETE http://localhost:5000/beers/1

